  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (COMPOUND-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package declares assuranceLevel High and decision Accepted despite multiple credibility factors where achievedLevel falls below requiredLevel, triggering COMPOUND-03 (assurance-level overstatement). The gap between declared assurance and structural evidence is the targeted weakness.",
  "assuranceLevel": "High",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/cou2-vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cou2-vad-absolute-hemolysis-prediction",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/cfd-hemolysis-centrifugal-pump",
