      "acceptanceCriteria": "Full SQA plan with version control, regression testing, and documented release procedures consistent with MRL 5 requirements.",
      "rationale": "SQA documentation is limited to version control logs; no formal regression test suite or release procedures are in place. Achieved level 2 is substantially below the required level 4 for a Class III device at MRL 5."
    },
    {
