      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy verification using manufactured solutions or analytic benchmarks across all relevant flow regimes.",
      "rationale": "Code verification was performed only on a simplified 2D channel flow; no manufactured-solution tests were conducted for rotating-frame turbulent hemolysis-relevant flows. Achieved level 2 falls short of required level 4."
