      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent on at least three systematically refined meshes with GCI reported for hemolysis index QoI.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation was performed but only on pressure drop; GCI for the hemolysis index itself was not reported. Achieved level 3 is one gradation below required level 4."
