      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental conditions must replicate all five VAD flow-speed combinations with physiologically representative blood analogue and full boundary condition documentation.",
      "rationale": "Experiments used a glycerol-water analogue at only three of five target operating points; boundary conditions at the inlet were estimated from vendor data rather than measured. Achieved level 3 is substantially below required level 5."
