      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs must map directly to clinical hemolysis endpoints accepted by regulatory guidance.",
      "rationale": "The normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) is used as the primary QoI, directly aligned with FDA guidance for VAD hemolysis assessment. Required level 4 is met."
