      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation geometry, operating conditions, and fluid properties must closely match the intended COU device and patient population.",
      "rationale": "Validation was conducted on the FDA generic pump geometry rather than the sponsor device; rotor speed range partially overlaps but does not cover the full clinical envelope. Achieved level 3 is below required level 5."
