      "acceptanceCriteria": "Hemolysis constitutive model must be validated against shear-exposure dose-response data; turbulence model sensitivity study required at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "The power-law hemolysis model was applied without sensitivity analysis to model-form uncertainty; turbulence model was fixed to k-omega SST without justification. Achieved level 2 is far below required level 5."
    },
