      "acceptanceCriteria": "Probability distributions assigned to all uncertain inputs; Monte Carlo propagation with convergence assessment.",
      "rationale": "Although Monte Carlo runs were performed, input distributions for blood viscosity and hemolysis model constants were assumed uniform without literature justification. Factor not fully assessed; achieved level 2 reflects incomplete UQ input characterization."
