    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concluded that the Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification and the breadth of validation activities, taken together, provide High assurance that the CFD hemolysis model is fit for the VAD COU. The team noted factor gaps but judged them collectively acceptable given the conservative hemolysis threshold applied. Decision: Accepted at High assurance level.",
